    "SUMMARY": "Timo Kern (born 16 January 1990) is a German professional footballer who plays as an attacking midfielder and captains Regionalliga Bayern club Bayern Munich II. \nHe began his career with Karlsruher SC and made his debut for the club in September 2010, as a substitute for Timo Staffeldt in a 2–0 defeat to FSV Frankfurt in the 2. Bundesliga."
